MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase:
In a space where we are alone, Brittany stares at me with flushed cheeks.
The silence exposes the sound of her slightly ragged breathing.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Conductor...

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase:
It seems that I am somewhat lacking in the sense of humor.
In fact, there was an incident that made me realize that...

I know that place well.
There's been a lot of talk about it among the train knights lately.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: This is..."The Broken Cuckoo Clock".
It is said that the store has a humorous performance, where they don't let you grab the ice cream and it keeps escaping, and when you think you have it, they only give you the bottom cone.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: M-more gags...? I understand. If you wish, Conductor.

No, I'm not saying that. I just don't know what to make of this one.
I want to see more gags.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I see that you are not laughing at me, so it's not good at all.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: What do you think? The key is to bring your fist in front of your chest and make a shaking gesture. Wasn't that interesting ......?
Haah...

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Brr, brr, brr, Brittany~

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Thank you very much. I'll start right away.
Well, fine, but...

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase:
In order to do that, I need to practice my gags.
So can you please watch me, Conductor?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I was so sorry. So, I did some research on humor so that I wouldn't make the same mistake again, and I learned that it is important to have a deeper understanding of gags.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase:
Everyone was in total shock.
I'll never forget the look on the children's faces.
...Seriously? Everyone must have been in shock. It's just ice cream.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I scolded the waitress in front of kids.
You didn't know and what?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: But I didn't know the systems of stores like that and I'm not familiar with them and...

What a cute little creature she is.
It's not funny by any means, but it does make you want to see more...

The visit has been timed to coincide with the end of the workday and everyone leaving.
It's obvious that she doesn't want the others to see her.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Please, watch my gag.
...Huh?
Of course. Come on, Brittany, give me your best gag!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Y-you still want to see?
Oh, this is going to be fun. Show more, show me more gags!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: H-how was it...?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: O-okay...! N-now I'm going to stand on my head...

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase:
It's a cuckoo clock, but for some reason, a rooster tells the time,
but the body moves like a pigeon!
―But that's good! Brittany, you're so cute!
I'll be honest. It's not funny at all.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Yes, it was a really funny store.

I see. It's definitely broken. It's quite a bold gag for a serious girl to do. Brittany's face is already bright red. I can clearly see that her sense of shame is in full swing. She must have a lot of determination.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Cock a doodle doo! Cock a doodle doo!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Cu, cu, cu, cuu!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Ko, ko, ko~!
With a serious expression, Brittany starts to rock her upper body back and forth, flapping her hands at the same time.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: The other day, I saw an unusual ice cream shop in town, where they perform tricks in front of the customers, or they don't give the customers their orders.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase:
Yes, this is a very important confession.
I couldn't muster the courage to speak to anyone but you, Conductor.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase:
No, you didn't mishear me.
It's true, you may have thought it was unexpected that I would do gags, though.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I am now supporting Iris Cloud.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Do you like it? Was I able to make you laugh...!?

Because of her pose, I can see different areas of Brittany,
which I normally can't, and I can't help but feel embarrassed.

I feel that if someone came in now, I would be in trouble for sure,
but in the end, I continue to appreciate Brittany's gags.
Brittany is embarrassed, but she never averts her eyes. I wonder what words her pretty lips will spell out next. No, I think I already know the answer.

Brittany throws her words at me while standing on her head.
Ah, I can't get enough...well, it's getting fun.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Brittany
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase:
Gag...It's a technique to make people laugh,
mainly performed by comedians.

I think I heard you wrong.
Can you ask me while staring at me again?
